            "summary": "Drowning in Plastic 版畫 / 76*52cm&nbsp; / 2019",
            "content_html": "\n    <h2 id=\"drowning-in-plastic\">\n      Drowning in Plastic\n    </h2>\n\n  <p>\n    <br>版畫 / 76*52cm&nbsp; / 2019<br>\n  </p>\n\n    <figure class=\"post__image post__image--center\">\n      <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/9/12Yuan-Su-Hai-Yang.jpeg\" height=\"4926\" width=\"3444\" alt=\"\"  sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" srcset=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/9/responsive/12Yuan-Su-Hai-Yang-xs.jpeg 300w ,https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/9/responsive/12Yuan-Su-Hai-Yang-sm.jpeg 480w ,https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/9/responsive/12Yuan-Su-Hai-Yang-md.jpeg 768w ,https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/9/responsive/12Yuan-Su-Hai-Yang-lg.jpeg 1024w\">\n      \n    </figure>",
