        {
            "id": "https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/homepage-6.html",
            "url": "https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/homepage-6.html",
            "title": "家庭樣本",
            "summary": "家庭樣本 互動裝置/依場地而定/2024年 木材、Esp32s、微型電腦、3D列印、馬達、螢幕 Interactive device / site-specific / 2024 Wood, ESP32s, microcomputers,&hellip;",
            "content_html": "\n    <h2 id=\"jia-ting-yang-ben\">\n      家庭樣本\n    </h2>\n\n  <p>\n    互動裝置/依場地而定/2024年<br>木材、Esp32s、微型電腦、3D列印、馬達、螢幕\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Interactive device / site-specific / 2024<br>Wood, ESP32s, microcomputers, 3D printing, motors, screens\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    當今社會對家庭的樣貌已經有更多元的認識，但我們還是可能在不知不覺中陷入「對理想家庭關係的美好想像」之中。然而「家庭」的結構並非本質性的，而是建構式、透過實踐堆疊而成的。「家庭樣本」這件作品模擬我們腦中「強迫性的美好家庭想像」，將工廠中對產品品質控管的邏輯套用在動態的家庭關係上，從反諷的視角提醒觀眾「沒有完美的家庭，家庭也沒有一定要怎樣」，並且放下對於家庭關係「應該」和「應當」的期待。<br>\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    In today's society, there is a more diverse understanding of the concept of family. However, we may still unconsciously fall into the trap of \"idealized family relationships.\" Yet, the structure of \"family\" is not inherent; rather, it is constructed through practice and accumulation. \"Family Samples\" simulates the compulsive idealized family image in our minds, applying the logic of product quality control in factories to dynamic family relationships. From a satirical perspective, it reminds the audience that \"there is no perfect family, and families don't have to be a certain way,\" urging them to let go of expectations about how family relationships \"should\" or \"must\" be.\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    游覺輔、賴玟霓\n  </p>\n\n  <div  class=\"gallery-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"gallery\" data-columns=\"3\">\n      <figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/_DSC6198.jpeg\" data-size=\"7008x4672\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/_DSC6198-thumbnail.jpeg\" height=\"512\" width=\"768\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/Xiao-Fang-Zi-Te-Xie.jpeg\" data-size=\"6166x4111\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/Xiao-Fang-Zi-Te-Xie-thumbnail.jpeg\" height=\"512\" width=\"768\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/Shou-Qu-Jian-Ce.jpeg\" data-size=\"7008x4672\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/Shou-Qu-Jian-Ce-thumbnail.jpeg\" height=\"512\" width=\"768\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/Zhu-Hua-Mian.jpeg\" data-size=\"4603x6904\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/Zhu-Hua-Mian-thumbnail.jpeg\" height=\"1152\" width=\"768\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/Te-Xiao-Fang-Zi.jpeg\" data-size=\"7008x4672\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/8/gallery/Te-Xiao-Fang-Zi-thumbnail.jpeg\" height=\"512\" width=\"768\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>",
