        {
            "id": "https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/homepage-4.html",
            "url": "https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/homepage-4.html",
            "title": "隨浪花昏沉",
            "summary": "隨浪花昏沉 隨浪花昏沉 單頻道音像 / 1280*720 / 2:40 / 2023年 Tochdesigner、Ableton Live Single-channel&hellip;",
            "content_html": "\n    <h2 id=\"sui-lang-hua-hun-chen\">\n      隨浪花昏沉\n    </h2>\n\n  <p>\n    隨浪花昏沉<br><br>單頻道音像 / 1280*720 / 2:40 / 2023年<br>Tochdesigner、Ableton Live\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    Single-channel audiovisual / 1280*720 / 2:40 / 2023<br>Tochdesigner, Ableton Live\n  </p>\n\n  <p>\n    「隨浪花昏沉 」發想自從新竹回到家鄉台東後的經歷，原以為去看海可以讓人放鬆身心， 結果因為還有事情沒有做完，去到的海岸也並非想像中的沙灘而是礫灘。海浪聲沒有撫慰我。 我反而注視著濺起的浪花，混雜著回到家的快樂，和一些難以言說的惆悵與慵懶的氣息。<br><br>/<br><br>\"Tossed Amidst the Waves\"<br><br>The inspiration for \"Tossed Amidst the Waves\" stems from my experiences returning to my hometown, Taitung, after being in Hsinchu. Initially, I thought a visit to the sea would bring relaxation to my mind and body. However, the reality differed as there were unfinished tasks, and the coastal area I arrived at was not the sandy beach I had imagined, but rather a pebble shore. The sound of the waves did not soothe me. Instead, I found myself fixated on the splashing seafoam, a mix of the joy of returning home and an indescribable sense of melancholy and languor.\n  </p>\n\n  <div  class=\"gallery-wrapper\">\n    <div class=\"gallery\" data-columns=\"3\">\n      <figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/6/gallery/Jie-Tu-2023-10-02-12.47.12.png\" data-size=\"1298x724\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/6/gallery/Jie-Tu-2023-10-02-12.47.12-thumbnail.png\" height=\"428\" width=\"768\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/6/gallery/Jie-Tu-2023-10-02-12.50.06.png\" data-size=\"2880x1554\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/6/gallery/Jie-Tu-2023-10-02-12.50.06-thumbnail.png\" height=\"414\" width=\"768\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/6/gallery/Jie-Tu-2023-10-02-12.50.35.png\" data-size=\"2880x1558\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/6/gallery/Jie-Tu-2023-10-02-12.50.35-thumbnail.png\" height=\"415\" width=\"768\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure><figure class=\"gallery__item\">\n      <a href=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/6/gallery/Jie-Tu-2023-10-02-12.51.32.png\" data-size=\"2880x1516\">\n        <img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://Jefff-yu.github.io/Jefffyu/media/posts/6/gallery/Jie-Tu-2023-10-02-12.51.32-thumbnail.png\" height=\"404\" width=\"768\" alt=\"\" >\n      </a>\n      \n    </figure>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <p>\n    <div class=\"post__iframe\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/m0U4ouG3fnQ?si=TPSbAgAY2S8I0gtG\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe></div>\n  </p>",
